<section class="sections-overview" id="sections">
<div class="sections-header reveal"><h2>Tes ressources de révision</h2><p>Programme, exercices par difficulté, indices progressifs et préparation orale</p></div>
<div class="section-cards stagger">
<a class="section-card section-card-full" data-theme="programme" onclick="showSection('programme')"><div class="card-number">00</div><div class="card-icon"><svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent-programme)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><path d="M16 2v4M8 2v4M3 10h18"/></svg></div><h3 class="card-title">Programme du cours</h3><p class="card-desc">Planning hebdomadaire avec thèmes, oral et exercices.</p><div class="card-tags"><span class="card-tag">Semainier</span></div><div class="card-arrow"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--text-muted)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="m7 17 10-10M7 7h10v10"/></svg></div></a>

<div class="section-separator"><h3>Scientifiques & Non-scientifiques</h3></div>

<a class="section-card" data-theme="analyse" onclick="showSection('analyse')"><div class="card-number">01</div><div class="card-icon"><svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent-analyse)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M3 3v18h18"/><path d="m6 15 5-5 3 3 6-6"/></svg></div><h3 class="card-title">Analyse</h3><p class="card-desc">Limites, dérivation, intégration + éq. différentielles.</p><div class="card-tags"><span class="card-tag">Exercices</span><span class="card-tag">Cours</span><span class="card-tag">Oral</span></div><div class="card-arrow"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--text-muted)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="m7 17 10-10M7 7h10v10"/></svg></div></a>
<a class="section-card" data-theme="fonction" onclick="showSection('fonction')"><div class="card-number">02</div><div class="card-icon"><svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent-fonction)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M4 12c2-4 5-6 8-3s5 1 8-3"/></svg></div><h3 class="card-title">Étude de fonction</h3><p class="card-desc">Tableaux de variation, asymptotes, extrema.</p><div class="card-tags"><span class="card-tag">Exercices</span><span class="card-tag">Cours</span><span class="card-tag">Oral</span></div><div class="card-arrow"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--text-muted)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="m7 17 10-10M7 7h10v10"/></svg></div></a>
<a class="section-card" data-theme="proba" onclick="showSection('proba')"><div class="card-number">03</div><div class="card-icon"><svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent-proba)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="7" height="7" rx="1.5"/><rect x="14" y="3" width="7" height="7" rx="1.5"/><rect x="3" y="14" width="7" height="7" rx="1.5"/><rect x="14" y="14" width="7" height="7" rx="1.5"/></svg></div><h3 class="card-title">Probabilités</h3><p class="card-desc">Lois, variables aléatoires, espérance.</p><div class="card-tags"><span class="card-tag">Exercices</span><span class="card-tag">Cours</span><span class="card-tag">Oral</span></div><div class="card-arrow"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--text-muted)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="m7 17 10-10M7 7h10v10"/></svg></div></a>
<a class="section-card" data-theme="geo" onclick="showSection('geo')"><div class="card-number">04</div><div class="card-icon"><svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent-geo)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="12,2 22,22 2,22"/><circle cx="12" cy="16" r="3"/></svg></div><h3 class="card-title">Géométrie</h3><p class="card-desc">Vecteurs, droites, plans, produit scalaire.</p><div class="card-tags"><span class="card-tag">Exercices</span><span class="card-tag">Cours</span><span class="card-tag">Oral</span></div><div class="card-arrow"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--text-muted)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="m7 17 10-10M7 7h10v10"/></svg></div></a>

<div class="section-separator"><h3>Scientifiques uniquement</h3></div>

<a class="section-card section-card-full" data-theme="algebre" onclick="showSection('algebre')"><div class="card-number">05</div><div class="card-icon"><svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent-algebre)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><path d="M3 9h18M3 15h18M9 3v18M15 3v18"/></svg></div><h3 class="card-title">Algèbre linéaire</h3><p class="card-desc">Matrices, espaces vectoriels, applications linéaires, diagonalisation.</p><div class="card-tags"><span class="card-tag">Exercices</span><span class="card-tag">Cours</span><span class="card-tag">Oral</span></div><div class="card-arrow"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--text-muted)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="m7 17 10-10M7 7h10v10"/></svg></div></a>
</div>
</section>
</div>

